OL,3,CGovernment addresses calls to improve
OL,4,C'outdated' animal cruelty laws
OL,6,FMr Noel adds: "Everyone in the
OL,7,Fcommunity knows that law is out of
OL,8,Fdate and I'm pleased to say States Vet
OL,9,Fhave already started and are quite a
OL,10,Flong way down the line in looking at
OL,11,Fthat law.
OL,13,F"The five domains of animal welfare
OL,14,Ftalk not just about the nutrition but
OL,15,Falso the physical environment, 'Does
OL,16,Fthe animal have appropriate shelter?
OL,17,FDoes it have a kennel if it's kept
OL,18,Foutside? Is it away from the elements?
OL,19,FDoes it have proper veterinary care?'.
