OL,3,CGovernment addresses calls to improve
OL,4,C'outdated' animal cruelty laws
OL,6,FThe JSPCA is looking for new ways to
OL,7,Fprotect animals, including an online
OL,8,Fforum.
OL,10,FMr Noel explains: "One of the things
OL,11,Fthat was suggested to us was the
OL,12,Frequirement for an anonymous web page
OL,13,Fwhere anyone around the island, if
OL,14,Fthey spot something that just isn't
OL,15,Fright about the care of a particular
OL,16,Fanimal, can post that to us. We treat
OL,17,Fevery single welfare concern that is
OL,18,Fraised seriously."
